      • syntheticAssociation

        @Nullable
public Meter.Id syntheticAssociation()
        For internal use. Indicates that this Id is tied to a meter that is a derivative of another metric. For example, percentiles and histogram gauges generated by HistogramGauges are derivatives of a Timer or DistributionSummary.

        This method may be removed in future minor or major releases if we find a way to mark derivatives in a private way that does not have other API compatibility consequences.

        Returns:
        The meter id of a meter for which this metric is a synthetic derivative.
